\fB                    Height :: integer(),\fR
\fB                    Option ::\fR
\fB                        {mask, boolean()} | {initialCount, integer()}.\fR

.br
.RS
.PP
Initializes the list.

.PP
See \fInew/3\fR for details.


.RE
.B
\fBdestroy(This :: wxImageList()) -> ok.\fR

.br
.RS
.PP
Destroys the object


.RE
