.RE
.B
\fBremoveAll(This) -> boolean() when This :: wxImageList().\fR

.br
.RS
.PP
Removes all the images in the list.


.RE
.B
\fBreplace(This, Index, Icon) -> boolean()\fR
\fB                 when\fR
\fB                     This :: wxImageList(),\fR
\fB                     Index :: integer(),\fR
